Key Match Events: Sacramento shot an abysmal 3-of-26 (11.5 percent) from beyond the arc, compared to 14-of-30 (46.7 percent) for the Clippers.
Post-Match Reflections: The Kings have found ways to score without hitting their threes, but going 3-of-26 makes it nearly impossible to win.
Against one of the best teams in the league, Sacramento will need to find a way to make more than three three-pointers.
